title: S Line
overview: A young woman with the ability to see mysterious red connections between lovers discovers her secret gift is no longer unique when special glasses granting similar powers appear on the black market.

tv.episodeOverview: Hyun-heup goes to Bangju High School after receiving a mysterious text message. There, he reunites with Seon-ah, a middle school classmate and Ji-wook's niece. However, Seon-ah is a victim of bullying from bullies. One day, when the bullying from bullies reaches its peak, Seon-ah discovers a mysterious pair of glasses in her locker...
